
* Options

option "title" "My Personal Finance"
option "operating_currency" "USD"
option "inferred_tolerance_default" "*:0.001"

plugin "beancount.plugins.auto_accounts"

* Accounts

; Edit this section to match your actual accounts and spending categories.
; bean-sync reads everything under "* Accounts" to guide LLM transaction categorisation.
; You can add sub-accounts freely (e.g. Expenses:Food:Groceries) — the LLM will use them.
; Account comments are also included as context, so add notes about what each account covers.

; --- Assets ---

1970-01-01 open Assets:Cash
1970-01-01 open Assets:Checking        ; Main chequing/checking account
1970-01-01 open Assets:Savings

; --- Income ---

1970-01-01 open Income:Paycheck
1970-01-01 open Income:Bonus
1970-01-01 open Income:InterestIncome
1970-01-01 open Income:Reimbursement

; --- Expenses ---

; Gas, parking, transit, rideshare, vehicle maintenance
1970-01-01 open Expenses:AutoAndTransport

; Phone, internet, electricity, water, recurring subscriptions
1970-01-01 open Expenses:BillsAndUtilities

; Consumer electronics, gadgets, cables, peripherals
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Electronics

; Gaming, streaming (Netflix, Spotify), cinemas, concerts
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Entertainment

; Bank fees, wire fees, currency conversion fees
1970-01-01 open Expenses:FeesAndCharges

; Restaurants, cafes, takeout, groceries, alcohol
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Food
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Food:Groceries
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Food:Restaurants

; Gym, sports, medical, dental, pharmacy
1970-01-01 open Expenses:HealthAndFitness

; Rent, mortgage, property tax, home maintenance, furniture
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Housing

; Anything that doesn't fit elsewhere
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Misc

; Retail purchases, clothing, online shopping
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Shopping

; Flights, hotels, Airbnb, car rental
1970-01-01 open Expenses:Travel

; --- Liabilities ---

; Add one entry per credit card. The LLM uses these account names.
1970-01-01 open Liabilities:CreditCard:MyCard    ; **** **** **** 1234

* Data

1970-01-01 open Equity:Initial

; bean-sync manages this file — run: bean-sync ingest  to regenerate after config changes.
; Only primary sources (enrichment: false) are included here.
; Do not edit sources/_primary.bean by hand.
include "sources/_primary.bean"
